data.text:
Presented by WPKN Radio Station, Park City Presents and Delmundo Productions

Join us for a night of rhythm, joy, and cultural fusion at the Park City Music Hall, 2926 Fairfield Avenue, Bridgeport, CT. The PasoFino Social Club will be bringing the Puerto Rican tradition of Parranda to life, with a twist that welcomes everyone to experience the magic.

Don't miss the chance to be a part of something truly special. Parranda Y Salsa will celebrate and cherish the beautiful cultural diversity of the Latin Holiday tradition. Featuring several special guests throughout the evening, this will be the event of the holiday season!

Mark your calendars for December 17th and spread the word! This holiday season, let's make memories, share traditions, and dance to the rhythm of unity.
